**Framer** | Mafia Power
__Basics__
The **framer** may choose one player each night to apply a *basic disguise* to. The player is disguised as an in-play mafia role. The **framer** may not disguise the same person on consecutive nights.

__Formalized__
Immediate Night: Weakly Disguise @Selection as @(AliveOnly:False,OrigAlign:Mafia)->RandomPlayer->OriginalRole (~NextNight) [Quantity: %Number%, Succession: No Target Succession]
